{"type": "article", "id": 3185, "title": "Urbanears x Marc系列联名耳机", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-31T08:05:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232812MwlNBfnWQrXKLcpv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自瑞士的新潮耳机品牌 Urbanears 日前邀请来了一位设计大师 Marc Jacobs ，为其带来全新的联名系列耳机。Marc Jacobs 选取了海洋、石油、浆果等大自然元素，将上述元素的色彩与纹理图案融入了耳机的设计之中，以石油为主题的头戴式耳机采用了黑白反差的耳机套，入耳式则搭配以粗糙的纹理。海洋主题运用了经典的海洋蓝，搭配以金色，更显质感；而浆果是以浆果红与银色的搭配呈现。入耳式款型定价 45 美元，头戴式款型定价 60 美元，<a href=\"http://www.urbanears.com/urbanears-x-marc-by-marc/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232810J2spME38Am7RcLdt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232810rV4Fq1Yl279Ijkd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232811MuFKlb5R9DaZeGQB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232811K5RaioNqxYu1DyrL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}